Privacy Policy for Master Converter

Effective Date: 08-10-2024

Master Converter is a Chrome extension that allows users to convert data files between various formats, including JSON, CSV, XML, YAML, and more, directly in their browser. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your data is handled securely.

Information Collection and Use

Master Converter does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. All conversions are processed locally on your device, ensuring your data remains private and secure. The extension does not connect to any external servers or services for processing.

Permissions

Master Converter requests the following permissions to function effectively:

File Access: To enable file conversion, the extension requires access to the files you select. This permission is used solely for processing selected files and not for any other purpose.
Storage: The extension may use local storage to save user preferences and settings for a better experience.
Security

We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information and ensure the safe operation of our extension. However, please be aware that no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or Master Converter, please contact us at befhobby@gmail.com.
